<item>
            <title>[DERBY-1214] JDBC4 calls in the Brokered* classes need to be forwarded to more capable classes.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-1214</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, the JDBC4 methods in the Brokered* classes raise SQLFeatureNotSupported. They should, where appropriate, forward their calls to more capable classes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12332103">DERBY-1214</key>
